FBIS3-7897 "dreeu040__a94013" FBIS-EEU-94-040-A Document Type:Daily Report 1 March 1994 ANNEX Czech Republic Havel Receives Sejm Official AU2802202394 Prague CTK in English 1838 GMT 28 Feb 94 AU2802202394 Prague CTK Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Lany, Central Bohemia Feb 28 (CTK) -- Technical and administrative aspects of the integration of the Czech Republic and Poland into the European Union were discussed on Monday [28 February] by Czech President Vaclav Havel and Speaker of the Polish Sejm (parliament) Jozef Oleksy, Oleksy told journalists. Oleksy said he spoke with Havel about pan-European matters, while he discussed more concrete concerns with other Czech representatives. The talks dealt generally with the European situation and integration, the Polish Constitution which is in preparation, the role of the president and the balance of power in the political system, Havel's spokesman Ladislav Spacek said.
